# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# open-geo .gitignore
# Everything generated, local, machine-specific, or maintainer-only. The
# product skill (.claude/skills/open-geo/), the capture-worker agent, i18n/,
# examples/, requirements.txt, and .claude-plugin/ stay committed; the
# maintainer-only docs and dev skills below are excluded (kept locally).
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# --- Maintainer-only — kept locally, excluded from the public repo ---
# AI/agent working notes + internal planning (for the maintainer, not users).
/CLAUDE.md
/RECENT_CHANGES.md
/ROADMAP.md
# Dev/maintenance skills (not part of the product; the open-geo skill stays).
.claude/skills/doc-sync/
.claude/skills/bug-hunt/
# Launch notes + personal smoke-test inputs.
/LAUNCH.md
/LAUNCH_POSTS.md
/*_smoke.csv
# Dogfood run notes (opengeo.pro measuring itself) — operational, maintainer-only.
/RUNBOOK-DOGFOOD.md
# Marketing / demo-video production (shot list, card generators, footage) —
# promo material, not part of the product. Kept local.
/media/

# --- Python ---
.venv/
venv/
env/
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/
.eggs/
build/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/

# --- Coverage (pytest-cov / coverage.py) ---
.coverage
.coverage.*
coverage.xml
htmlcov/
*-coverage.txt

# --- Local SQLite databases (recreated via seed_demo / runs) ---
data/*.db
data/*.db-wal
data/*.db-shm
data/*.sqlite
data/*.sqlite3
data/*.bak*
# throwaway fixture DBs (e.g. data/_fixture_dash.db)
data/_*.db

# --- Captured run artifacts (visible-Chrome captures) ---
data/screenshots/
data/responses/

# --- Generated reports (recreated by report.generate) ---
reports/*.pdf
reports/*.png

# --- Font build cache (upstream variable fonts pulled by fonts/build.py) ---
# The subsetted .ttf faces + OFL licenses under fonts/ stay committed; only the
# large upstream downloads used to regenerate them are ignored.
fonts/.cache/

# --- Node ---
/node_modules/

# --- Dashboard frontend (Node) ---
dashboard/web/node_modules/
dashboard/web/dist/
dashboard/web/.vite/
*.tsbuildinfo

# --- OS / editor junk ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~

# --- IDE project dirs (machine-specific) ---
.idea/
.vscode/

# --- Logs ---
*.log

# --- Local Claude Code settings (machine-specific; skills stay committed) ---
.claude/settings.local.json
# Debugger / run configs — machine-specific dev convenience, in any .claude/ dir
# (the committed skill under .claude/skills/ stays tracked)
**/.claude/launch.json

# --- Secrets / local env (never commit to a public repo) ---
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
# local override files anywhere (e.g. dashboard/web/.env.local)
*.local

# --- Personal / scratch query inputs ---
# The canonical shared sample is examples/questions.csv (kept committed). Drop
# your own real or scratch query lists here without committing them.
examples/test_queries.csv
# Real-market audit inputs (the user's own questions.csv, not the Example demo),
# plus their harvest provenance docs (<name>_rationale.md).
/mattress_questions.csv
/dogfood_questions.csv
/*_questions*.csv
/*_rationale.md

# Growth content pack (draft posts) + outreach/recon notes — kept local,
# not part of the public repo.
/GROWTH_PACK.md
/GROWTH.md
/OUTREACH_*.md
/*_RECON_HANDOFF.md
/vc_posts/
